N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 7 ยง 5.53 - Names of previous recipients

State Regulations

Upon request, an individual whose record has been corrected
shall be given the names of all known agencies, individuals or organizations to
whom the erroneous or incomplete data has been given. Notes
